{
  "stem": "25912.5",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "But, you know, we had a floor to sleep on, and that was all you could have.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "We really were very, very short of money, to the extent that we would, we went to the soup kitchen as a Jewish relief, whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We also said, gave our names, so that they could be broadcast that we had survived.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "But I remember an occasion-- probably more than one occasion-- when we went to buy a plate of soup in [? a cafe ?], and asked for a plate of soup and two plates.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Sorry-- a plate of soup and two spoons, because we couldn't afford any more than that.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, there was nothing there to go to.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "What for?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was nothing left of our apartments.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, in fact, my grandparents' apartment was standing, but you know, I don't know who was there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There wouldn't have been anything of ours left.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't-- No, because everything was lost in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think whatever there was which we-- my mother took, and my grandparents took.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "As I said, the bracelet, which, I was told, weighed half a kilo, I left behind, cleverly, probably was taken off my grandmother in Treblinka.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So there was, there was nothing to go back to.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just had what we were standing in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, one day, we were walking in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly, a car stopped.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was the a pre-war friend of my parents, Gustaw Werfel, who recognized Mother and was delighted to see her, asked what we were doing and what was happening to us.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I think he might, he was deported to Russia.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In any case, he was a director of the Polish Repatriation Institute, which was in Lodz.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
